    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts a linear power delivery via its six individual throttle bodies and remains planted thanks to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The critical VANOS system has been professionally addressed, and the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. While the exterior displays a light patina expected of a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain is robust, and the suspension geometry remains precise. A compelling opportunity for the purist seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
